        "Contractor|RecoverSpaceDescriptionIntro": [
            "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------\n\nRed Wind is excited to announce that we are looking to hire new couriers to help with deliveries across the \u2019verse. We pride ourselves on been a flexible company that\u2019s eager to meet the needs of all clients, everywhere. We\u2019ll ask no questions; if you want it there, we\u2019ll get it there. If that sounds like you, we have an introductory contract to see if you\u2019re the right fit.\n\nWe need a resilient new hire to head to <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>, recover the package abandoned by a former employee, and finish the delivery.\n\nPACKAGES TO RECOVER\n     \u00b7 <EM4>1x [Item1]</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATION\n     \u00b7 Deliver to <EM4>[Destination|Target|Address]</EM4>\n\nIf you\u2019re able to handle this contract we\u2019d be delighted to send you more courier opportunities.\n\nTAKE PRIDE IN YOUR WORK \u2013 Even as a contractor you are representing Red Wind Linehaul. Do not intentionally do anything to harm the company\u2019s reputation."
